DANE4CDN a Firefox extension, which shows the demo of explict delegation from
web site to CDN provider by extending DANE protocol.

DANE4CDN extension relies on the following DNS libraries:
  - libunbound (2.1.5)
  - libldns (1.6.16)
Users must install these two DNS libraries before using DANE4CDN extenstion.

After installing DANE4CDN extension successfully, users may access the following
URL to see how DANE4CDN works (which is shown by Figure dane4cdn.png).

Web site demo: https://dane4cdn.cdnsec.info
